{"data":{"page":{"id":"f67e590e-b186-506b-851d-8843ac9e319f","html":"<p>While I was working at WCRS, I got involved in several prototypes and promotional ideas for SKY. One of the prototypes involved R&#x26;D with Javascript and CSS to animate the panels of the following design. I built a few responsive demos with reactive and unfolding animations. When the panels were clicked, the new sections would reveal themselves and push the other panels to the border of the screen.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bf8a23dae225c8e00485aeec74fb08af/40247/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/bf8a23dae225c8e00485aeec74fb08af/6b333/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bf8a23dae225c8e00485aeec74fb08af/f3ce7/1.jpg 200w,\n/static/bf8a23dae225c8e00485aeec74fb08af/72342/1.jpg 400w,\n/static/bf8a23dae225c8e00485aeec74fb08af/6b333/1.jpg 800w,\n/static/bf8a23dae225c8e00485aeec74fb08af/40247/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/850e90feb95d462d7b414e9f1110196f/40247/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 60.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/850e90feb95d462d7b414e9f1110196f/6b333/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/850e90feb95d462d7b414e9f1110196f/f3ce7/2.jpg 200w,\n/static/850e90feb95d462d7b414e9f1110196f/72342/2.jpg 400w,\n/static/850e90feb95d462d7b414e9f1110196f/6b333/2.jpg 800w,\n/static/850e90feb95d462d7b414e9f1110196f/40247/2.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9da7322ed083272247cb25b410fdbcc2/40247/3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/9da7322ed083272247cb25b410fdbcc2/6b333/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9da7322ed083272247cb25b410fdbcc2/f3ce7/3.jpg 200w,\n/static/9da7322ed083272247cb25b410fdbcc2/72342/3.jpg 400w,\n/static/9da7322ed083272247cb25b410fdbcc2/6b333/3.jpg 800w,\n/static/9da7322ed083272247cb25b410fdbcc2/40247/3.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>I also built a prototype with folding panels, which uses CSS3 to create the panel shadows dynamically.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4adecea33aadf7d2f325f00a69f45673/40247/4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 91.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/4adecea33aadf7d2f325f00a69f45673/6b333/4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4adecea33aadf7d2f325f00a69f45673/f3ce7/4.jpg 200w,\n/static/4adecea33aadf7d2f325f00a69f45673/72342/4.jpg 400w,\n/static/4adecea33aadf7d2f325f00a69f45673/6b333/4.jpg 800w,\n/static/4adecea33aadf7d2f325f00a69f45673/40247/4.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>The highlight of these prototyping works was a installation demo I built using OpenFrameworks and Microsoft Kinect to promote the new Disney Channel in Sky [<strong>video coming soon</strong>]. The demo app tracks the hand of the user and translate the movements into Tinkerbell’s magic dust, therefore the user can move Tinkerbell with his hands. It uses a particle system, shaders, blur and other graphic techniques to increase the visual appeal.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/afe2c2e0d54f2d31a3382672afe0d69c/40247/5.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"5\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/afe2c2e0d54f2d31a3382672afe0d69c/6b333/5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/afe2c2e0d54f2d31a3382672afe0d69c/f3ce7/5.jpg 200w,\n/static/afe2c2e0d54f2d31a3382672afe0d69c/72342/5.jpg 400w,\n/static/afe2c2e0d54f2d31a3382672afe0d69c/6b333/5.jpg 800w,\n/static/afe2c2e0d54f2d31a3382672afe0d69c/40247/5.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>","fields":{"prefix":"2013-04-06"},"frontmatter":{"title":"SKY prototypes","cover":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/sky/","source":"work"}}